[MESSAGE]Through the tutorials, you will familiarize yourself with the basic aspects of running your very own restaurant empire!

It is important that you pay attention to the animated arrows that appear on the screen, as they will point to important buttons or other tutorial subjects.

If for any reason you would like to exit the game, press the _Esc_ key anytime to access the game menu.

_Left-click_ on the _Next button_ to proceed.
